data.description: STUNNING TOWNHOME NEAR WALKING PARK! This immaculate home of 2,894 SF features 4 bedrooms two of which could be master suites and 3 gorgeous baths along with a 2 car garage. The main floor boast an open concept with stunning views even while living within city limits and near many school. A spectacular basement is the greatest surprise of all with a theater room including stadium seating, a projector and surround sound system all awaiting your future enjoyment. The lower level master suite provides a walk through closet, large spa like bath with a huge shower including two separate shower heads and body sprays. The gorgeous flooring, large dining and spacious kitchen make entertaining a dream. Just outside the back door you will find a comfortable deck for enjoying an evening with family and friends. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from the previous listing. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
